						               													<description>Get ready to add some spice to your game night with Spicy Games! &amp;#10;Each of the spice bottles hold all of the pieces you need to play a game. Each game takes 2 minutes to learn and 10 minutes to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sweeten your fun with Sugar Cubes, the quick and easy game of words and wit. Sprinkle out the dice and spoon on a little creativity to beat the timer and taste sweet victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a turn, a player rolls all 8 dice and then turns them so they can see the letters. The player to their right flips the timer.&amp;#10;The active player then has 20 seconds to come up with a grammatically correct sentence. Each word must start with one of the letters shown on the dice. While making the sentence, the player lines up the dice in the order they have used them in.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players score 5 points for each die used.&amp;#10;If a player manages to use 7 dice they score 40 points.&amp;#10;If a player uses 8 dice they score 50 points&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the most points after 7 rounds wins&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
